*Bolesti* su česti problemi čovečanstva. (Diseases are common problems of mankind.)

Ljudi se bore sa raznim *bolestima*. (People struggle with various diseases.)

Neke *bolesti* se mogu sprečiti. (Some diseases can be prevented.)

Postoje lekovi za lečenje određenih *bolesti*. (There are medicines for treating certain diseases.)

Neke *bolesti* su neizlečive. (Some diseases are incurable.)

U savremenom svetu, *bolesti* se često prenose preko putovanja. (In the modern world, diseases are often spread through travels.)